Privacy Policy
Effective Date: August 13th, 2025

1. Introduction
Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you make a purchase through our website using Stripe as our payment processor. By using our services, you agree to the terms outlined here.

2. Information We Collect
When you place an order, we may collect:

Name
Email address
Billing and shipping address
Payment details (processed securely by Stripe)
Order details and purchase history
3. How We Use Your Information
We use your information to:

Process and fulfill your orders
Communicate with you about your purchase
Provide customer support
Improve our products and services
Comply with legal obligations
4. Payment Processing via Stripe
We use Stripe to process payments securely. Stripe collects and processes your payment information in accordance with its own Privacy Policy. We do not store your full credit card details on our servers.

5. Data Sharing
We do not sell or rent your personal information. We may share your data only with:

Service providers (such as Stripe) to complete transactions
Shipping carriers to deliver your order
Legal authorities if required by law
6. Data Security
We take reasonable measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, use, or disclosure. However, no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure.

7. Your Rights
Depending on your location, you may have the right to:

Access, update, or delete your personal information
Object to certain uses of your data
Request a copy of the data we hold about you
8. Changes to This Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated effective date.

9. Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or how your data is handled, please contact us at:
